headline: This Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stock Has Jumped 30% Already in 2025. It Could Jump Another 32%, According to Wall Street.
summary: Shares of Micron Technology (NASDAQ: MU) have gotten off to a hot start in 2025, gaining an impressive 30% as of this writing and outpacing the 8% gains clocked by the PHLX Semiconductor Sector index.  Micron carries a 12-month median price target of $145, according to 42 analysts covering the stock.  The company ended 2024 on a sour note.
